## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

* PCF Healthwatch does not cover the recently recommended [MySQL KPIs for PCF v1.12](https://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/1-12/monitoring/kpi.html#kpi4MySQL).
* PCF Healthwatch does not cover monitoring of [Isolation Segments](https://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/1-12/adminguide/isolation-segments.html).
* PCF Healthwatch is intended to monitor only the PCF foundation it is installed on.
* Currently, only the Google Chrome browser is supported when accessing the product UI.
* If an alpha version of PCF Healthwatch is installed, it must be deleted before proceeding with the installation of the beta tile.

